{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775838820819,"sessionID":"ses_287c3dd97ffex6UHN98QkAnthn","part":{"id":"prt_d783d0ad0001ZVvPKTCsN69KOW","messageID":"msg_d783c7a95001a2dK8XdG0lZgI6","sessionID":"ses_287c3dd97ffex6UHN98QkAnthn","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-001/design.md","content":"# AR-001 Design: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n\n## Overview\n\nDefine the Go types for the AgentRuntime Custom Resource Definition (CRD).\n\n## API Group\n\n- Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- Version: `v1alpha1`\n- Kind: `AgentRuntime`\n\n## Type Definitions\n\n### AgentRuntime\n\nRoot type representing the AgentRuntime CRD.\n\n### AgentRuntimeSpec\n\nSpecification of the desired state for an AgentRuntime.\n\n### AgentRuntimeStatus\n\nCurrent observed state of the AgentRuntime.\n\n## Design Decisions\n\n> TBD: Document key design decisions here.\n\n## References\n\n- [Kubernetes Custom Resources](https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/extend-kubernetes/api-extension/custom-resources/)\n- [Kubebuilder CRD Markers](https://book.kubebuilder.io/reference/markers/crd.html)\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-001/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-001/design.md","time":{"start":1775838820798,"end":1775838820818}}}}
