{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775838820823,"sessionID":"ses_287c3dd97ffex6UHN98QkAnthn","part":{"id":"prt_d783db529001E7bnZpmpBOiSpy","messageID":"msg_d783c7a95001a2dK8XdG0lZgI6","sessionID":"ses_287c3dd97ffex6UHN98QkAnthn","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:10","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-001/notes.md","content":"# AR-001 Notes & References\n\n## Context\n\nThis change defines the foundational CRD types for the AgentRuntime resource.\nThe AgentRuntime CRD is central to the AgentCube platform as it represents\na sandbox runtime environment for AI agents.\n\n## Conventions\n\n- JSON tags: camelCase (e.g., `json:\"agentImage\"`)\n- Go structs: PascalCase (e.g., `AgentImage`)\n- API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- Version: `v1alpha1`\n\n## Related Changes\n\n> Link to related ARs once they exist.\n\n## Open Questions\n\n> Document any open questions or decisions pending.\n\n## References\n\n- [Kubernetes CRD Documentation](https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/extend-kubernetes/api-extension/custom-resources/)\n- [controller-runtime](https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/controller-runtime)\n- [code-generator](https://github.com/kubernetes/code-generator)\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-001/notes.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-001/notes.md","time":{"start":1775838820806,"end":1775838820822}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775838821755,"sessionID":"ses_287c3dd97ffex6UHN98QkAnthn","part":{"id":"prt_d783cbc5c0018TmaUop4wh7Lz7","messageID":"msg_d783c7a95001a2dK8XdG0lZgI6","sessionID":"ses_287c3dd97ffex6UHN98QkAnthn","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-001/spec.yaml","content":"id: AR-001\ntitle: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\nmodule: pkg/apis\nlanguage: Go\nsize: S\nstatus: open\n\n# AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime Type Definitions\n# Module: pkg/apis\n# Language: Go\n# Size: S\n\n# OpenSpec Metadata\nopenspec:\n  version: \"1.0\"\n  project: agentcube\n\n# Architecture Requirement\nrequirement:\n  type: crd-definition\n  description: |\n    Define the AgentRuntime Custom Resource Definition (CRD) types for the\n    runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1 API group. This includes the\n    Go struct definitions for AgentRuntimeSpec, AgentRuntimeStatus, and\n    related sub-resources.\n\n# Scope\nscope:\n  in:\n    - pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go\n    - pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go updates\n    - pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go\n  out:\n    - Controller implementation\n    - Webhook validation\n    - CRD YAML manifests (generated)\n\n# Acceptance Criteria\nacceptance:\n  - AgentRuntime types compile without errors\n  - Types follow Kubernetes CRD conventions\n  - JSON tags use camelCase\n  - Go structs use PascalCase\n  - DeepCopy methods generated\n\n# References\nreferences:\n  - https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/extend-kubernetes/api-extension/custom-resources/\n  - https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/controller-runtime\n\n# Estimation\nestimation:\n  size: S\n  story_points: 2\n  days: 1\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-